"title": "6603: acceptance, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6603",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's gracious favour shown both to Israel and to the Gentiles. God accepts people who respond to him, and worship that is offered sincerely and is accompanied by wholehearted commitment.</p>\n<h2>God's acceptance of human beings</h2>\n<h3>God's gracious acceptance of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:23\">2KI 13:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:40-Ezek20:41\">EZK 20:40–20:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:1\">ROM 11:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's acceptance of those who respond to him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:7\">GEN 4:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:27\">EZK 43:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:37\">JHN 6:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:38\">EXO 28:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:3\">ROM 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10-2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's acceptance of the Gentiles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:6-Isa56:7\">ISA 56:6–56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34-Acts10:35\">ACT 10:34–10:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7-Acts15:8\">ACT 15:7–15:8</a></p>\n<h3>Prayers for acceptance by God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:8\">DEU 21:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:23\">2SA 24:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's acceptance of human worship</h2>\n<h3>Acceptable sacrifices</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:19-Lev22:21\">LEV 22:19–22:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:3-Lev1:4\">LEV 1:3–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:5-Lev19:7\">LEV 19:5–19:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:27-Lev22:29\">LEV 22:27–22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:3-Mal3:4\">MAL 3:3–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:23\">JHN 4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:18\">PHP 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:16\">HEB 13:16</a></p>\n<h3>Acceptance of gifts offered for the tabernacle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:5\">NUM 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:51-Num31:54\">NUM 31:51–31:54</a></p>\n<h3>Unacceptable offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:10-Jer14:12\">JER 14:10–14:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:18\">LEV 7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:25\">LEV 22:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:8-Mal1:10\">MAL 1:8–1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:13\">MAL 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Acceptable service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:6-Ps51:7\">PSA 51:6–51:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:19-Jer6:20\">JER 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:17-2Cor6:18\">2CO 6:17–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:11\">ISA 52:11</a></p>\n<h3>God accepts prayer and praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:9\">PSA 6:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:15\">HEB 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:26\">JOB 33:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:8-Job42:9\">JOB 42:8–42:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:108\">PSA 119:108</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:13-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:13–18:14</a></p>",
